# JavaScript

Read [app/javascript/AGENTS.md](../../app/javascript/AGENTS.md) and [docs/FRONTEND.md](../../docs/FRONTEND.md).

- Default: server-rendered HTML; add JS only when needed.
- Stimulus in `app/javascript/controllers/`; register in `index.js`.
- Prefer `data-*` attributes over fragile selectors.
- No new npm deps unless explicitly requested.
- Do not run build commands unless explicitly requested.

